scene.message:
Nanjo: ...Where are we?{wait_fr:60}{nl}
Ah, {ctl0f:1},{nl}
you're safe.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Y-yeah!{nl}
I'm alive!{nl}
{ctl08:65281}Our leader pulls through!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...Where are we?{nl}
Ah, {ctl07:1}...{nl}
Are you uninjured?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ...Ow!!{nl}
That's it, I'm going home!{nl}
Why does this happen?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: It seems everyone{nl}
is uninjured.{nl}
Truly remarkably lucky.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...This is{nl}
our school gym.{nl}
From six months ago...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: ...Hey, isn't this{nl}
our school gym?!{nl}
From six months ago too...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ...Isn't this{nl}
Ayase's school gym?{nl}
Six months back? That one?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Came back?{nl}
Six months ago?!{nl}
Get together, Sonoda!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...A time slip?{nl}
Quite different from{nl}
what your mother said.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: ...I keep saying this,{nl}
but I really have no mom.{waitkey}To think what{nl}
Yosuke was saying...{nl}
it was all true...{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Oh! There you are!{nl}
Terrible news, Maki!{nl}
Naito-kun got hurt bad!{waitkey}That black girl{nl}
came again...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: No way!{nl}
Wh-what?!{nl}
Yosuke-kun!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Yosuke-kun...{nl}
Is that Naito Yosuke?{waitkey}{clearbox}I recall he and Kasai Chisato{nl}
went missing about{nl}
2 months ago.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Yosuke... is that{nl}
Naito Yosuke?{waitkey}He ran off with his{nl}
girlfriend Kasai{nl}
2 months ago, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Yosuke...{nl}
is that Naito Yosuke?{waitkey}Didn't he run off{nl}
with Kasai about{nl}
2 months ago?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...That fool{nl}
acting alone in this...{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, let's chase Sonoda.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{ctl0f:1},{nl}
don't Sonoda's actions{nl}
seem odd for amnesia?{waitkey}{clearbox}Is this really{nl}
six months back...?{nl}
That girl came for Sonoda.{waitkey}But six months ago,{nl}
Sonoda was{nl}
in the hospital.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...Naito{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
...I see.{nl}
...Oh — what is it, {ctl0f:1}?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: A timeslip...{nl}
{ctl07:1},{nl}
do you believe it?{waitkey}I feel like something's{nl}
different here.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: But is this{nl}
really school?{nl}
Maybe somewhere else.{waitkey}Yeah! It's a dream!{nl}
Wahaha!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: "Time strip"?{nl}
Is that a new thing?{nl}
Is it trending?{waitkey}{clearbox}That's wild!{nl}
Is Ayase{nl}
falling behind?!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: I think Maki{nl}
likes Naito-kun.{nl}
Such a perfect couple!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Excuse me —{nl}
how many days until{nl}
the sports festival?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Rude as always.{nl}
One month left.{nl}
Amnesia, Nanjo-kun?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: ...You really{nl}
have amnesia?!{nl}
We're all second years!{waitkey}I need to tell{nl}
everyone!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...Same year too.{nl}
More puzzling{nl}
than ever.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Ha ha ha...{nl}
You appeared from{nl}
nowhere...{waitkey}Must be my imagination!{nl}
Ha ha ha!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...Hey,{nl}
isn't this the school gym?{nl}
From six months ago...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: H-hey Sonoda! ...{nl}
Naito — the one missing{nl}
2 months ago?{waitkey}{ret}
